# moblies-shop — UI/UX Design System

**Last updated:** 2026-06-21  
**Scope:** Frontend only — no backend/API/server action changes.

---

## Typography

### What changed
- Replaced Geist fonts with **Inter** (Latin) + **IBM Plex Sans Arabic** (Arabic).
- RTL body uses Arabic font first; LTR uses Inter first.

### Where applied
- `app/layout.tsx` — font loading via `next/font/google`
- `app/globals.css` — `--font-sans` token chain

### Why / impact
- Professional SaaS readability in both Arabic and English.
- IBM Plex Sans Arabic is a high-quality Arabic UI font with proper glyph support.

---

## Color System (SaaS Neutral Palette)

### What changed
- Primary: indigo `#4f46e5` (light) / `#818cf8` (dark) — Stripe/Shopify admin feel.
- Semantic tokens: `--success`, `--warning`, `--destructive` with tinted badge backgrounds.
- Subtle borders: `border-border/60` for reduced visual noise.

### Where applied
- `app/globals.css` — CSS custom properties
- `components/ui/badge.tsx` — semantic color variants
- `components/dashboard/stat-card.tsx` — accent icon backgrounds

---

## Spacing & Layout Shell

### What changed
- `--sidebar-width: 16.5rem`, `--header-height: 3.75rem`
- `.app-shell-main` — subtle indigo radial gradient background
- `.page-container` — max-width 1400px centered content
- Sticky header with backdrop blur

### Where applied
- `app/(dashboard)/layout.tsx`
- `components/layout/sidebar.tsx` — Header component

### Impact
- Cleaner dashboard hierarchy; content doesn't stretch edge-to-edge on wide screens.

---

## Navigation UX

### What changed
- Sidebar grouped into: Main, Inventory, Operations, Analytics, Administration.
- Active nav item: primary fill + shadow.
- Header shows user name + role badge.
- Mobile bottom nav: icon pill highlight on active tab.
- Language switcher: segmented pill toggle (AR / EN).

### Where applied
- `components/layout/nav-config.ts` — `NavGroup`, `getGroupedNavItems()`
- `components/layout/sidebar.tsx`
- `components/layout/mobile-bottom-nav.tsx`
- `components/layout/language-switcher.tsx`
- `messages/ar.json`, `messages/en.json` — `nav.groups.*`

### Impact
- Reduced cognitive load; faster wayfinding for 15+ routes.

---

## UI Primitives (components/ui/)

### Button (`button.tsx`)
- Rounded-lg, shadow-sm on primary, `loading` prop with spinner, active scale feedback.

### Card (`card.tsx`)
- rounded-xl, softer border, added `CardFooter`.

### Table (`table.tsx`)
- Muted header row, uppercase column labels, `text-start` for RTL, tighter row padding.
- Removed outer scroll wrapper — use `DataTableShell` instead.

### Dialog (`dialog.tsx`)
- Backdrop blur, rounded-xl, text-start headers, logical `end-*` close button.

### Tabs (`tabs.tsx`)
- Pill-style list with rounded-xl container, active tab shadow.

### Badge (`badge.tsx`)
- Rounded-md, tinted semantic colors via CSS vars (not hardcoded emerald/amber).

### Input (`input.tsx`)
- rounded-lg, ring-offset focus (unchanged pattern, consistent with tokens).

### Label (`label.tsx`)
- Explicit foreground color for contrast.

---

## New Reusable Components

| Component | Path | Purpose |
|-----------|------|---------|
| `DataTableShell` | `components/ui/data-table-shell.tsx` | Bordered table container + optional footer count |
| `FormSection` | `components/ui/form-section.tsx` | Grouped form fields with title + grid columns |
| `FormField` | `components/ui/form-section.tsx` | Label + field wrapper |
| `LoadingSpinner` | `components/ui/loading-spinner.tsx` | Inline/page loading indicator |
| `EmptyState` | `components/ui/empty-state.tsx` | Dashed empty state with icon + action slot |

### Usage pattern for list pages
```tsx
<DataTableShell footer={`${items.length} items`}>
  <Table>...</Table>
</DataTableShell>
```

