## Page-Level Improvements

### Dashboard (`app/(dashboard)/dashboard/page.tsx`)
- Stat cards with colored icon accents.
- EmptyState for no recent sales / low stock.
- Quick links to POS and products.

### Products (`app/(dashboard)/inventory/products/page.tsx`)
- DataTableShell wrapper, EmptyState when no products, tabular-nums for prices.

### Login (`app/(auth)/login/login-client.tsx`)
- Brand icon, gradient background, pill language switcher, loading button.

### Reports date filter (`reports/reports-date-filter.tsx`)
- Card-wrapped filter form with labeled inputs.

### Customers / Stock movements
- DataTableShell + EmptyState on customers and movements pages.
- Movements filter uses Card + Input + Button (consistent with reports filter).

